":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:51:25.000Z","msg":"真係典型等餵王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a8c46cd2978ab0ffd260646ae71fa7845cf63d","tid":561214,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T21:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4312a0c724e9f918c21a72c4430af14de2a7908b","tid":561214,"uid":90515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107216973b05649055bd6442a2408da6c7cfaa8c","tid":561214,"uid":158317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T23:36:26.000Z","msg":"笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127e62c9a5e490feed2b1cca049e49cf6e040cd1","tid":561214,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T23:36:39.000Z","msg":"狗都入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205252adca8cfb04da45d94427d6ab57b396fc89","tid":561214,"uid":47023,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:06:14.000Z","msg":"俾狗入兩粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a275c6f75c388bde184f139bd41da91dd9f8487d","tid":561214,"uid":51951,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"忽探子來報：&ldquo;尼馬引巴黎下關，用球靴挑着法甲冠軍赤幘，來班拿貝前大罵搦戰。&rdquo;施丹曰：&ldquo;誰敢去戰？&rdquo;摩納哥背後轉出驍將法卡奧曰：&ldquo;小將願往。&rdquo;丹喜，便著法卡奧出馬。即時報來：&ldquo;法卡奧與尼馬戰不三合，被尼馬斬了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n眾大驚。軒歷基斯曰：&ldquo;吾有上將占士，可斬尼馬。&rdquo;丹急令出戰。占士手提拜仁上馬。去不多時，飛馬來報：&ldquo;占士又被尼馬斬了。&rdquo;眾皆失色。<br />\n<br />\n丹曰：&ldquo;可惜吾上將hazard，Harry Kane未至！得一人在此，何懼尼馬！&rdquo;言未畢，階下一人大呼出曰：&ldquo;吾願往斬尼馬頭，獻於帳下！&rdquo;眾視之，見其人身長九尺，聲如巨鍾，立於帳前。正是牙朗。<br />\n<br />\n牙朗曰：&ldquo;如不勝，請斬某頭。&rdquo;丹教釃熱酒一杯，與牙朗飲了穿靴。牙朗曰：&ldquo;酒且斟下，某去便來。&rdquo;出場提衫，飛身頭槌。眾球迷聽得場內鼓聲大振，喊聲大擧，如天摧地塌，嶽撼山崩，眾皆失驚。<br />\n<br />\n正欲探聽，鸞鈴響處，馬到中軍，牙朗提尼馬之頭，擲於地上。其酒尚溫。後人有詩讚之曰：<br />\n <br />\n 　　威鎮巴黎第一功，三連歐聯響冬冬。<br />\n<br />\n　　牙朗停盞施英勇，酒尚溫時斬尼馬。"},{"pid":"0f364d99f06a3d8ff61f73f80eb8b1f274281104","tid":561214,"uid":27597,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"佢已經去到靠十二碼同依啲執雞去入波<br />\n罰球離譜<br />\n幾球炒飛機<br />\n馬些路傳中靚到pk，以佢以前既能力一定食硬<br />\n總結，馬些路仲好波過牙朗"},{"pid":"6c36d310e69a2bba9f44aa3a6f02346f5c3e4273","tid":561214,"uid":47544,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0f364d99f06a3d8ff61f73f80eb8b1f274281104","tid":561214,"uid":27597,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"佢已經去到靠十二碼同依啲執雞去入波<br />\n罰球離譜<br />\n幾球炒飛機<br />\n馬些路傳中靚到pk，以佢以前既能力一定食硬<br />\n總結，馬些路仲好波過牙朗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"真心上年啲搶點tap in同頭鎚仲好勁<br />\n今年跌哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c94091ff67739200e0a0cbd4e01a1f164da68c","tid":561214,"uid":6577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09225d872e8ac6ee2c69c628143cad478c115bd","tid":561214,"uid":171177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"633ffe98f042be678e72eaf6aeab2b5282d5abb1","tid":561214,"uid":734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0652928afe49578d9f79e84ca2a617930c5f07","tid":561214,"uid":29916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6